{
  "stem": "16571.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 379.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they was from about nine, 10, to 17.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were taken on this train, as I was saying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Private train.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Never saw a train like that before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "With seating, with windows, with-- you know, what the train where we went on was cattle trains, 150 people, no seats.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Sitting more or less in-- in each other's laps to make room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I believe there was some straw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then sort of a year later, to be taken on a train like a civilian train.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I just didn't know what was happening.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I've never been on a-- a train like that before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it just took everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Go here, go there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On that train, as I said, I don't really quite know because we-- we left-- because of the interruption of the bombings, we-- I should imagine anything from eight, 10, 12, or even 14 hours, until we are arrived in this-- at night, nighttime, which I learned later was Hanover, near Celle, actually.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This place where we-- we were taken into-- when we arrived in Hanover-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] now I'm getting myself mixed up.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It might have been Celle, the nearest big town to where eventually I finished up in, which was, as I said, Belsen.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But considering that we were only in the camps about 13 and 1/2 months, Hungarians, what we were at the time-- and I learned later that some of my friends, Polish, were in there three, four, five years.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was lighter for me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was the hardest 15 or 18 months of the war, because the Germans by then were being pushed back from the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they themselves were short of food, and all that.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
